    This is the project's most aggressive deletion. Hold the line on the single atomic commit per CRIT-6 — splitting into "delete first, replace second" leaves master in a broken state mid-PR. Pre-flight the call-site inventory thoroughly; missed consumers cause hard-to-diagnose runtime failures.
